dct_title_s: Map of the Manasquan River showing the exterior lines for solid filling and for piers
dct_description_sm: Map covers area from Horse Point to Stump Point along the Manasquan River. Map shows the exterior lines for solid filling and for piers and includes water depths, as well as the riverfront properties of Chadwick Davis, B. Hill, Sam S. Osborne, R. Clark, W. Curtis, Hugh Harding, Sylvanous Jenkins, and Thomas Cook.
